OL,3,CPetrol, showering, or food? Brutal
OL,4,Cchoices forced on young people
OL,6,F"You can't afford to have showers
OL,7,Fevery single day. You can't afford to
OL,8,Fkeep clean - and then people make fun
OL,9,Fof you for not being clean enough."
OL,11,FThose are the words are the reality
OL,12,Ffor 18-year-old Iris, who has spoken
OL,13,Fto ITV News West Country about the
OL,14,Fsevere impact the cost of living
OL,15,Fcrisis is having on her.
OL,17,FShe is one of five young people who
OL,18,Fhave opened up about their experiences
OL,19,Fand the huge financial pressure they
OL,20,Ffeel every single day.
