OL,3,CPetrol, showering, or food? Brutal
OL,4,Cchoices forced on young people
OL,6,FEarlier this week, ITV News heard from
OL,7,FSaskia, a mother who skips breakfast
OL,8,Fand lunch as she struggles to clothe
OL,9,Fher toddler, and Chloe, a young
OL,10,Fbusiness owner who has been left
OL,11,Ffeeling suicidal as she feels she
OL,12,F"works endlessly" but still cannot
OL,13,Falways afford to shower.
OL,15,FNow Iris, Chloe, and Robert - who are
OL,16,Fbeing supported by Bristol charity
OL,17,F1625 Independent People - are sharing
OL,18,Ftheir stories.
