OL,3,CPetrol, showering, or food? Brutal
OL,4,Cchoices forced on young people
OL,6,FRobert is 22 years old and now has a
OL,7,Fjob - but even with an income, money
OL,8,Fis always on his mind.
OL,10,F"It's stressful," he said. "It's lots
OL,11,Fof sleepless nights trying to figure
OL,12,Fout when you can do this, or when you
OL,13,Fcan do that.
OL,15,F"Even now I am earning money, with
OL,16,F(the cost of) food and petrol going
OL,17,Fup, each month I'm still like 'can I
OL,18,Factually afford to do that? Can I
OL,19,Fafford to put that much petrol in this
OL,20,Fweek?'
OL,26,@xD@ApmxD@Mpn
