OL,3,CPetrol, showering, or food? Brutal
OL,4,Cchoices forced on young people
OL,6,F"It's mentally draining."
OL,8,FHe added: "I can't save for insurance.
OL,9,FI've got no money from the bills I've
OL,10,Fgot on credit. I'm paying #91 a month
OL,11,Fon that. Interest is where you lose
OL,12,Fall your money.
OL,14,F"My advice is if you can't buy
OL,15,Fsomething outright - don't buy it.
OL,16,FThat's what I've learnt to go by."
OL,18,FSimilarly 18-year-old Iris, who is a
OL,19,Fcare leaver, says budgeting is all-
OL,20,Fconsuming.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/12
