OL,3,CPetrol, showering, or food? Brutal
OL,4,Cchoices forced on young people
OL,6,FShe said: "It's hard to budget for
OL,7,Fthings when you're unaware if there's
OL,8,Fgoing to be an emergency."
OL,10,F"I spend #35 a week shopping," she
OL,11,Fadded. "But sometimes I need to get
OL,12,Flike laundry detergent, fabric
OL,13,Fconditioner, toilet paper, toothpaste
OL,14,F- maybe a new toothbrush, some
OL,15,Fhaircare or body stuff.
OL,17,F"Sometimes you have to miss out on
OL,18,Fcertain food aspects - or sometimes
OL,19,Fyou might not be able to have a shower
OL,20,Ffor a few days or not do any laundry.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/12
