OL,3,CPetrol, showering, or food? Brutal
OL,4,Cchoices forced on young people
OL,6,F"I want to see someone high up in the
OL,7,FGovernment live on the money we have
OL,8,Fbecause it's not a lot. It's not
OL,9,Fpossible.
OL,11,F"Especially for care leavers like
OL,12,Fmyself as soon as you turn 18 you are
OL,13,Fdropped. You're not given much
OL,14,Fsupport. you're not taught anything
OL,15,Freally.
OL,17,F"No one teaches you how to cook a
OL,18,Fhealthy, balanced meal, how to budget
OL,19,Fyour money properly, how to do
OL,20,Flaundry, how to do just basic things."
