OL,3,CPetrol, showering, or food? Brutal
OL,4,Cchoices forced on young people
OL,6,FFor Chloe, who is 19 and a care
OL,7,Fleaver, she described it as a "massive
OL,8,Fstruggle". She's trying everything to
OL,9,Ftry and help her situation, including
OL,10,Fenrolling in courses.
OL,12,FShe added: "You have to sacrifice. You
OL,13,Fhave to choose your priorities."
OL,15,FShe believes schools should do more to
OL,16,Fteach people life skills, as 1625
OL,17,FIndependent People is doing.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/12
