OL,3,CPetrol, showering, or food? Brutal
OL,4,Cchoices forced on young people
OL,6,F"(Schools) don't teach us life
OL,7,Fskills," she said. "They don't teach
OL,8,Fus about credit, they don't teach us
OL,9,Fabout paperwork.
OL,11,F"They don't teach us how to write
OL,12,Femails, they don't teach us any of the
OL,13,Ftaxes, vehicles, the list goes on.
OL,15,F"Most of the things I use now I did
OL,16,Fnot learn from school. I asked from
OL,17,Fasking adults, from organisations like
OL,18,FCitizens Advice. These things you
OL,19,Fwouldn't know about unless you ask.
OL,20,FAnd then who do you ask?"
OL,26,@nD@BpmnD@JpnwD@AOU
