OL,4,Cchoices forced on young people
OL,6,FShe added: "I think an even bigger
OL,7,Fissue for us as care leavers is trying
OL,8,Fto learn all the life skills. It makes
OL,9,Fyou (financially) worse off in the
OL,10,Fend."
OL,12,F1625 Independent People is supporting
OL,13,Fall the people we've spoken to, but as
OL,14,Fthe cost of living bites it says it is
OL,15,Ffeeling the pressure on its services.
OL,17,FThe charity works with those leaving
OL,18,Ffoster care and at risk of
OL,19,Fhomelessness, teaching people life
OL,20,Fskills such as cooking and helping
OL,21,Fwith housing and emotional support.
OL,26,@qD@EpmqD@Qpn
