OL,3,CPetrol, showering, or food? Brutal
OL,4,Cchoices forced on young people
OL,6,FIts CEO Dom Wood told said the current
OL,7,Fsituation is about as bad as it gets -
OL,8,Fparticularly in Bristol where the cost
OL,9,Fof living is so high.
OL,11,FHe said: "It's pretty dire. Young
OL,12,Fpeople are being hit by financial
OL,13,Faffects in every direction.
OL,15,F"Bristol particularly is one of the
OL,16,Fmost expensive places to live - in
OL,17,Fterms of the cost of renting in
OL,18,Frelation to what you can get from
OL,19,Fhousing benefit if you're in low paid
OL,20,Fwork or unemployed.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G10/12
