OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F434A1734007177
OL,3,CPetrol, showering, or food? Brutal
OL,4,Cchoices forced on young people
OL,6,F"If you combine that with effects on
OL,7,Ffood and utilities - there's a massive
OL,8,Feffect on young people at the moment.
OL,10,F"They don't see how they'll get out of
OL,11,Fany kind of financial pressure into
OL,12,Fthe future. The financial burden seems
OL,13,Flike a never ending source of angst."
OL,15,FThe charity helps more than 1,500
OL,16,Fpeople every year, but it says it is
OL,17,Fstruggling to help everybody as the
OL,18,Fcost of living crisis worsens.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G11/12
