OL,3,CPetrol, showering, or food? Brutal
OL,4,Cchoices forced on young people
OL,6,FMr Wood said: "The funding we have
OL,7,Ffrom local authorities, there's a
OL,8,Fhierarchy of needs of who gets through.
OL,10,F"We subsidise that with the funding we
OL,11,Fhave ourselves to meet as many
OL,12,Fpeople's needs as we can. But with an
OL,13,Fincreasing number of needs, there are
OL,14,Fpeople with lower level needs that
OL,15,Faren't getting support and they may be
OL,16,Fthe people that need to call on
OL,17,Fservices at a later stage."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G12/12
